<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Mi vialte nih Baibal ca rel, Kan i tinhmi si cio ko seh, Khuaza kip ah
 a than hlan tiang, Thli nih kalpi lengmang ko seh.

[C1]
   Rili le fing tlang vialte ah, Pathian bia sung rung ceu ko tuah, Zan
   mui lak ah a vak mi hna, Pathian sin ah an phak hlan tiang.

[V2]
 A phaknak kipah a ceunak, Ni bangin a tlang zungzal ko, Sual
 riantuannak kha a tei i, Muihnak khuadawm kha a tian dih.

[C2]
   Rili le fing tlang vialte ah, Pathian bia sung rung ceu ko tuah, Zan
   mui lak ah a vak mi hna, Pathian sin ah an phak hlan tiang.

[V3]
 Kan Pa Pathian hmai a langhter, Ngaihthiam dawtnak he a ceu ko, Adam
 phun tlau ciami sinah, Van hnangamnak bia kha a chim.

[C3]
   Rili le fing tlang vialte ah, Pathian bia sung rung ceu ko tuah, Zan
   mui lak ah a vak mi hna, Pathian sin ah an phak hlan tiang.

[V4]
 Lung retheimi a dinhter hna, Ngaihchiami an hna a ngamter, Lungdermi
 thazang a thawnter, Zungzal ruahchannak a pek hna.

[C4]
   Rili le fing tlang vialte ah, Pathian bia sung rung ceu ko tuah, Zan
   mui lak ah a vak mi hna, Pathian sin ah an phak hlan tiang.</lyrics>
<key>Bb</key>
<title>MI KIP CA BAIBAL THIANG CH197</title>
<hymn_number>197</hymn_number>
</song>